3452704357319_520685078_o.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7d10ff5df5a48e0cea9d07c3c16be049c19f0dda_2_800x569.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"569\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7d10ff5df5a48e0cea9d07c3c16be049c19f0dda_2_800x569.jpg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7d10ff5df5a48e0cea9d07c3c16be049c19f0dda_2_1200x853.jpg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7d10ff5df5a48e0cea9d07c3c16be049c19f0dda_2_1600x1138.jpg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7d10ff5df5a48e0cea9d07c3c16be049c19f0dda_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">14923080_1123452704357319_520685078_o.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">2000×1424 394 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
