      "cooked": "<p>bukur e luajten rolin “kur ziheshin” e “kundershtoheshin” pastaj te dy dilshin balli i kazanit <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=5\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"></p>\n<p>Sa per refugjatet, Trump me  e arrira. tamam druvar</p>",
