      "created_at": "2017-06-14T03:43:34.912Z",
      "cooked": "<p>po ta shofesh me kujdes ky nuk ka bo udheheqesit e botes, por, si çdo artist tjeter, ka bo turinin e vet.</p>\n<p>Psh ktu nuk ka bo Obamen, ose me sakte ka bo i çik Obamen, por kryesisht ka bo turinin e vet si fizionomi ly me karaboje:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/0f4ab3a7312aca6722c99272eaad2eb6b13ff546.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"718\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
